2: Hyper-realistic photograph of a rustic wooden shed in a lush English cottage garden. Vibrant flowers in full bloom, including red roses, purple lavender, and yellow sunflowers. A winding stone path with moss-covered edges leads to a weathered oak door with black iron hinges. Dappled sunlight filters through overhanging trees. Clear azure sky with wispy cirrus clouds. Golden summer afternoon light. Soft shadows and depth of field. Canon EOS R5, 24mm f/1.4 lens, ISO 100, impeccable detail and texture.
3: Ultra-high definition photograph of a sleek, contemporary garden shed in a meticulously designed modern English garden. Minimalist concrete path leading to a frameless glass door. Geometric plantings of ornamental grasses, lavender, and sculptural topiary. Raised cor-ten steel planters with architectural succulents. Clean lines and monochromatic color scheme with pops of purple and silver foliage. Immaculate lawn as a green canvas. Subtle landscape lighting. Bright summer day with clear cerulean sky. Shot with a Sony A1 camera, 16-35mm f/2.8 G Master lens, showcasing razor-sharp details and perfect exposure.
